                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 723.2515/196.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                            <gloss type="to">American Minister to Peru</gloss>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>, <lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1910-11-22">
                            <hi rend="italic">November 22, 1910</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Your November 21. Repeat your November 19 to the Legations at La Paz, Santiago,
                    Quito, Buenos Aires, and Embassy at Petropolis, indicating source of
                    information; and continue keeping those missions informed.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Knox</hi>.</signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
